  m_Name: Level_01_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelIntroData
  levelTitle: Wild Boar Invasion
  levelContext: 'Wild boar are spreading across the grasslands.


    Escaped from
    farms, they now roam freely, tearing up soil, destroying habitats, and pushing
    out native species. With no effective predators, their population is growing
    fast.


    And breeding season is near.


    If they aren''t contained in time,
    their numbers will explode, making control nearly impossible.


    <color=#FF0000><size=30><b>Mission:</b></size>

    <size=23>Track
    and contain the herds before they multiply.</size></color>'
